title: Week 8 NFL Recap, Analysis; Poor Coaching Around the League (Football 10/28)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 8 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 13 games on the Sunday slate including Packers-Chiefs (1:45), Panthers-49ers (15:20), Browns-Patriots (24:35), Raiders-Texans (34:15), Broncos-Colts (40;20), Chargers-Bears (46:15), Eagles-Bills (59:00), Bengals-Rams (1:03:30), Bucs-Titans (1:08:30), Cardinals-Saints (1:13:30), Seahawks-Falcons (1:19:00), Giants-Lions (1:25:30) and Jets-Jaguars (1:29:30).
